<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Privacy Policy | 1A Administration Dashboard</title>
    <meta content="1A Website" property="og:title" />
  <meta content="Welcome to 1A!" property="og:description" />
  <meta content="https://1a75.org/privacy" property="og:url" />
  <meta content="https://cdn.xanderxx.xyz/1a-logo.png" property="og:image" />
  <meta content="#4b5a2a" data-react-helmet="true" name="theme-color" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/custom.css">
    <style>
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding-left: 0.7rem;
                padding-right: 0.7rem;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 1.08rem;
            }
            ul, p {
                font-size: 0.98rem;
            }
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/navbar", { user, active }) %>
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin-top: 3rem;">
        <h1 class="mb-4" style="color: var(--ranger-gold);">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>
        <h2 style="color: var(--ranger-gold);">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Discord user ID, username, and avatar (when you log in).</li>
            <li>Event and certification data you create or manage.</li>
            <li>Server and channel IDs for event posting.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2 style="color: var(--ranger-gold);">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide and improve the Service.</li>
            <li>To manage events, certifications, and Discord integrations.</li>
            <li>To ensure security and prevent abuse.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2 style="color: var(--ranger-gold);">3. Data Sharing</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties.</li>
            <li>Data may be shared with Discord as required for bot functionality.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2 style="color: var(--ranger-gold);">4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
            We retain your data as long as necessary to provide the Service. You may request deletion of your data by contacting us.
        </p>
        <h2 style="color: var(--ranger-gold);">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
            We use session cookies for authentication and security. No tracking or advertising cookies are used.
        </p>
        <h2 style="color: var(--ranger-gold);">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>You may request access to or deletion of your data at any time.</li>
            <li>Contact us at <a href="mailto:main@xanderxx.xyz">main@xanderxx.xyz</a> for requests.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2 style="color: var(--ranger-gold);">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be posted on this page.
        </p>
        <h2 style="color: var(--ranger-gold);">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>
            For questions, contact the server administrators or email: <a href="mailto:main@xanderxx.xyz">main@xanderxx.xyz</a>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Back to Home</a>
        </p>
    </div>
    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>